21:23.667 --> 21:25.167
Shut the fuck up, Hera.

23:13.875 --> 23:16.417
Dammit. Sergeant Pepper!

23:16.417 --> 23:18.917
Shit.

23:18.917 --> 23:20.125
Hera!

23:20.125 --> 23:23.042
Uh...

23:27.542 --> 23:28.792
Pepper!

23:40.917 --> 23:42.917
Hi.
Hey, how's it going?

23:42.917 --> 23:45.292
Oh, it's going.

23:45.292 --> 23:46.417
What are you doing?

23:46.417 --> 23:50.042
I am trying to do laundry.

23:50.042 --> 23:52.542
Fun. How's Marcus?

23:52.542 --> 23:55.917
He's Marcus. He's
happy we're here.

23:55.917 --> 23:57.125
And you?

23:58.292 --> 24:01.042
I don't know yet. I
mean, it's beautiful.

24:01.042 --> 24:03.542
But I tried to paint yesterday

24:03.542 --> 24:05.417
and I just ended up
staring at the canvas

24:05.417 --> 24:07.125
for, like, an hour
before I gave up.

24:07.125 --> 24:08.917
Hey, you'll get

24:08.917 --> 24:10.917
your inspiration back.

24:10.917 --> 24:14.292
Julie, please
let me help you.

24:14.292 --> 24:16.000
Stand clear of the door.

24:16.000 --> 24:18.417
Oh.

24:19.542 --> 24:21.167
Huh. Thank you.

24:21.167 --> 24:23.000
My pleasure, Julie.

24:23.000 --> 24:24.292
Who are you talking to?

24:24.292 --> 24:25.917
Oh, nobody.

24:25.917 --> 24:28.542
It's Marcus's upgraded toy

24:28.542 --> 24:32.125
or, as he likes to call
it, his virtual assistant.

24:32.125 --> 24:33.500
Hey,
shoot. I gotta go.

24:33.500 --> 24:34.917
The kids are getting
into some trouble,

24:34.917 --> 24:37.000
but promise you'll
call me every day.

24:37.000 --> 24:38.042
- I promise.
- Okay.

24:38.042 --> 24:39.167
I will talk to you tomorrow.

24:39.167 --> 24:40.292
I love you. Bye.

24:43.667 --> 24:44.667
She seems fine to me.

24:44.667 --> 24:46.292
You leaving
after just getting there

24:46.292 --> 24:48.542
isn't going to be easy on her.

24:48.542 --> 24:51.250
She will be fine, okay?

24:51.250 --> 24:53.375
I think we've made
some progress.

24:53.375 --> 24:55.917
Marcus, I don't
think this is a good idea.

24:55.917 --> 24:57.542
Can't you postpone this?

24:59.125 --> 25:00.417
Uh, Doc, can we postpone
my payments to you?

25:00.417 --> 25:02.292
You know what, why
don't we just postpone

25:02.292 --> 25:05.542
all my fucking expenses until
we figure this thing out?

25:05.542 --> 25:08.375
Look, it's only five days.
What about what I need?

25:09.667 --> 25:13.250
I will make it up to her
when I get back.

25:14.375 --> 25:15.625
You know what, I think
our session's up.

25:15.625 --> 25:17.375
Thank you for your time, Doctor.

25:17.375 --> 25:19.417
But I need to pack
for my flight.

25:19.417 --> 25:21.167
Marcus.

25:21.167 --> 25:22.042
Fuck!

25:26.667 --> 25:28.167
I'm home!

25:28.167 --> 25:29.542
In the kitchen.

25:32.125 --> 25:34.500
That smells delicious.

25:34.500 --> 25:36.042
It'll be ready in 10.

25:39.125 --> 25:42.417
So how's the rest
of your morning?

25:42.417 --> 25:44.250
Do anything interesting?

25:44.250 --> 25:45.042
Not really.

25:46.292 --> 25:48.042
Still getting used
to this house.

25:48.042 --> 25:51.292
Mm-hmm.

25:51.292 --> 25:52.542
How was your meeting?

25:53.917 --> 25:57.042
Uh, yeah, I mean, they
loved my presentation

25:57.042 --> 25:59.250
and the main investor
is excited to meet me

25:59.250 --> 26:00.500
when I get to Hong Kong.

26:02.042 --> 26:04.042
How long are you
going for again?

26:04.042 --> 26:06.667
Five days. So no wild parties.

26:06.667 --> 26:08.042
Not until I get back.

26:09.667 --> 26:13.417
Can you grab my pain
pills outta my purse?

26:13.417 --> 26:14.917
My ankle's killing me today.

26:16.167 --> 26:17.542
How many have you had today?

26:18.625 --> 26:19.917
This is my second.

26:21.042 --> 26:22.917
Oh, how
about just half?

26:23.750 --> 26:24.625
Sure.

26:30.625 --> 26:33.417
Hey, uh, you didn't
move any crypto coins

26:33.417 --> 26:35.667
from our wallet
account, did you?

26:35.667 --> 26:36.917
No. Why?

26:38.042 --> 26:40.292
Well, 20K crypto
coins missing.

26:40.292 --> 26:44.125
Well, I wouldn't even know
what to do with crypto coin.

26:44.125 --> 26:49.125
I mean, did you call a bank
or wherever you keep it?

26:50.042 --> 26:50.667
Yeah, I'll look into it.

26:58.125 --> 27:00.417
Okay, well, I'll call
you when I get there.

27:00.417 --> 27:02.542
Okay. Well, I'll
have a safe trip.

27:02.542 --> 27:05.750
Marcus, it's time to go.

27:05.750 --> 27:07.000
My driver's here.

27:07.667 --> 27:09.292
I'll miss you.

27:12.500 --> 27:15.625
Well, don't worry
because I'll be watching.

27:15.625 --> 27:16.500
Creep.

27:17.750 --> 27:19.042
Bye, Hera.

27:19.042 --> 27:20.292
Have fun, Marcus.

27:49.542 --> 27:50.792
Love you, babe.

27:50.792 --> 27:51.875
Love you.

27:51.875 --> 27:53.750
Sweet dreams, babe.

28:18.750 --> 28:19.625
Okay.

29:08.292 --> 29:08.875
Hmm.

30:21.917 --> 30:24.500
Hmm.

30:24.500 --> 30:26.667
Well, hello.

30:26.667 --> 30:30.917
Pepper, which one of these
dresses should I keep? Hmm?

30:30.917 --> 30:32.667
I don't need both.

30:32.667 --> 30:33.917
This one?

30:35.042 --> 30:35.875
This one?

30:37.542 --> 30:39.750
Okay. Okay.

30:39.750 --> 30:41.542
I'm just gonna get
a second opinion.

30:46.667 --> 30:48.792
Hey, I have a dilemma.

30:48.792 --> 30:51.000
Well, you know
you make your best decisions

30:51.000 --> 30:52.625
after a shot of whiskey.

30:52.625 --> 30:53.792
Well, I was hoping

30:53.792 --> 30:54.542
you could help me.

30:54.542 --> 30:56.375
Oh, sure.

30:56.375 --> 30:57.625
Yeah, I'm better than booze.

30:57.625 --> 31:00.542
Hey, guys, keep it
down! I'm on the phone!

31:00.542 --> 31:04.917
I need you to tell me which
one of these I should keep.

31:04.917 --> 31:06.875
Uh, none?

31:06.875 --> 31:09.042
What do you mean
none? I like them.

31:09.042 --> 31:10.667
Where are
you gonna wear them to?

31:10.667 --> 31:13.667
The annual harvest moon
forest gathering or...

31:13.667 --> 31:16.292
Okay, it's a little isolated,

31:16.292 --> 31:18.542
but it's not Siberia
for God's sake.

31:18.542 --> 31:20.750
Okay. I'm sorry.

31:20.750 --> 31:22.792
I mean, the nearest
little town's 10 miles

31:22.792 --> 31:24.667
and the city's 30.

31:24.667 --> 31:25.667
It's not so bad.

31:27.042 --> 31:28.667
Although there's no Lyft.

31:28.667 --> 31:30.667
What? Okay, but Uber?

31:30.667 --> 31:31.667
Mm-mm.

31:31.667 --> 31:32.792
So where's Marcus?

31:32.792 --> 31:34.917
Is he playing with
his little toys?

31:34.917 --> 31:37.375
Uh, he just left
for Hong Kong.

31:37.375 --> 31:38.292
What?

31:38.292 --> 31:40.917
Yeah, he had to go.

31:40.917 --> 31:42.917
Some deal they're closing.

31:42.917 --> 31:45.000
Okay, well,
I'm just really surprised

31:45.000 --> 31:46.417
he left you so soon.

31:46.417 --> 31:48.375
Yeah, I'm kinda pissed off.

31:48.375 --> 31:50.917
We were actually
getting closer, I think.

31:50.917 --> 31:54.000
Mm, but it's not
very sensitive if you ask me.

31:54.000 --> 31:56.750
Hey, come and stay
with us for a few days,

31:56.750 --> 31:57.875
just until he gets back.

31:57.875 --> 32:00.042
- I don't know.
- Come on.

32:00.042 --> 32:02.917
It'll be fun. I miss my roomie.

32:02.917 --> 32:06.042
Really? Yeah, you
know what, why not?

32:06.042 --> 32:07.625
Can I bring Pepper?

32:07.625 --> 32:09.292
Yeah, you better
bring that handsome boy.

32:09.292 --> 32:11.500
Okay. I'll see you tomorrow.

32:11.500 --> 32:13.917
See you tomorrow!

32:17.375 --> 32:18.042
Okay.

32:20.375 --> 32:21.042
Mm.

32:22.917 --> 32:26.292
Hey, babe. I was just
about to tell you my plans.

32:26.292 --> 32:28.917
Yeah, what's going
on? You're packing a bag?

32:28.917 --> 32:30.125
Yeah.

32:30.125 --> 32:32.375
Um, I'm gonna go
and stay with Sophie

32:32.375 --> 32:33.875
and the kids until you get back.

32:35.125 --> 32:36.500
Look, Jules,
I don't feel comfortable

32:36.500 --> 32:38.375
with you driving
six and a half hours

32:38.375 --> 32:39.875
with a broken ankle
whilst you're on meds.

32:39.875 --> 32:41.542
I just don't think it's safe.

32:42.917 --> 32:46.667
So you can have a change
of plans, but I can't?

32:46.667 --> 32:49.417
I don't wanna be here, Marcus.

32:49.417 --> 32:52.542
I'm alone and it's
quiet. I don't like it.

32:52.542 --> 32:53.750
Yeah,
but Dr. Tate says

32:53.750 --> 32:55.000
that you need quiet right now.

32:55.000 --> 32:57.042
Okay, can you please
stop doing that?

32:57.042 --> 32:59.667
I feel like everyone is
telling me what to do.

32:59.667 --> 33:01.375
Okay.
Okay, I'm sorry.

33:03.042 --> 33:04.500
You know I love you, right?

33:06.792 --> 33:08.542
Yeah, I love you too.

33:08.542 --> 33:10.042
And I
miss you already.

33:12.375 --> 33:13.542
Where are you now?

33:13.542 --> 33:15.875
Oh, I'm
just in my hotel room.

33:15.875 --> 33:17.167
What did you do today?

33:17.167 --> 33:18.000
Not much.

33:18.917 --> 33:23.042
I got to relax and,
um, I tried to paint.

33:23.042 --> 33:25.417
That's good.
That makes me happy.

33:26.625 --> 33:28.167
Okay, well, I've got a
meeting in 10 minutes.

33:28.167 --> 33:29.875
I just wanted to
call and say hi.

33:30.875 --> 33:32.042
Good luck.

33:32.042 --> 33:33.542
Thanks.
Talk tomorrow?

33:33.542 --> 33:34.417
Mm-hmm.

33:43.417 --> 33:44.542
I love you, Julie.

33:47.417 --> 33:48.417
Goodnight.

33:52.875 --> 33:55.542
And stop talking to me
through the cameras, please.

35:58.917 --> 36:00.167
Julie.

36:06.292 --> 36:07.167
Julie.

37:02.292 --> 37:03.167
Hi.

37:04.667 --> 37:06.042
Marcus?
Hey.

37:06.042 --> 37:07.917
Hey, what are you doing up
in the middle of the night?

37:07.917 --> 37:09.917
I was taking a nap
and Hera woke me up.

37:12.167 --> 37:13.625
I heard a man's voice.

37:13.625 --> 37:15.167
What? Who?

37:15.167 --> 37:16.250
I don't know, I just...

37:16.250 --> 37:18.792
I know that I heard someone.

37:18.792 --> 37:20.167
I thought there was
someone in the house.

37:20.167 --> 37:21.292
Wait, wait, wait, wait. What?

37:21.292 --> 37:22.792
What happened? What?

37:22.792 --> 37:24.667
Well, I heard
him saying my name

37:24.667 --> 37:29.292
and then there was, like,
footsteps and glass breaking.

37:31.917 --> 37:33.792
Julie, you
know that's not possible.

37:33.792 --> 37:35.667
Well, I know what
I heard, Marcus.

37:35.667 --> 37:38.417
Babe, it's just another
one of your bad dreams, okay?

37:38.417 --> 37:41.000
No. No, no, I was awake.

37:41.000 --> 37:45.292
I was, and when I heard the
glass break in the kitchen,

37:45.292 --> 37:49.292
I came out and
there was nothing.

37:50.417 --> 37:53.292
Listen,
you're stressed, okay?

37:53.292 --> 37:55.167
Because you're home
alone in the move and-

37:55.167 --> 37:56.042
No.

37:57.000 --> 37:59.875
No, Marcus I heard a voice.

37:59.875 --> 38:01.292
Why don't you believe me?

38:01.292 --> 38:02.917
Julie, I can
see all the camera footage

38:02.917 --> 38:04.792
inside the house and
it's just you there.

38:04.792 --> 38:06.042
So why don't you take a pill

38:06.042 --> 38:08.000
and try to relax and
go back to sleep?

38:08.000 --> 38:10.292
And meanwhile I'll run a
security system's check

38:10.292 --> 38:12.167
and make sure
everything's running fine.

38:12.167 --> 38:14.000
You know, maybe, maybe there was

38:14.000 --> 38:15.417
some interference or something.

38:19.292 --> 38:20.167
Okay.

38:21.125 --> 38:22.292
I miss you.

38:22.292 --> 38:23.417
Hera, run
a full diagnostics

38:23.417 --> 38:25.667
on the security system
inside the house.

38:25.667 --> 38:29.042
I'm running a full
diagnostics now, Marcus.

38:29.042 --> 38:31.667
Sorry for the bother, Hera.

38:31.667 --> 38:33.125
No problem, Julie.

38:34.292 --> 38:37.292
See? Get some rest.

38:37.292 --> 38:38.292
Goodnight.

38:38.292 --> 38:40.750
Okay, goodnight.

38:47.292 --> 38:48.792
Pepper?

38:48.792 --> 38:50.167
Pepper.

38:51.500 --> 38:52.792
Are you in the laundry?

38:54.292 --> 38:56.750
What are you doing
in there, silly?

38:58.792 --> 39:00.750
Hey, come here.

39:03.417 --> 39:06.042
Let's go back to bed, huh?

39:48.000 --> 39:48.917
What the...

39:58.042 --> 39:59.417
Oh, Jesus Christ.

40:01.292 --> 40:03.042
Hera, turn off alarm.

40:05.542 --> 40:07.292
Hera, turn off alarm!

40:14.417 --> 40:18.292
Okay.

40:28.542 --> 40:29.917
Hello.

40:29.917 --> 40:33.292
Hi. Yeah, I think my
thermostat's broken.

40:33.292 --> 40:34.417
Actually, I know it is.

40:36.375 --> 40:38.417
No, it's brand new.
We just moved in.

40:40.125 --> 40:41.500
It's Julie Alexander.

40:43.542 --> 40:45.417
Today? Yeah.

40:56.417 --> 40:59.167
Hey, Soph. I'm so sorry.

40:59.167 --> 41:00.167
Hey, what's wrong?

41:00.167 --> 41:01.875
I thought you were coming over?

41:01.875 --> 41:02.875
Yeah, I know.

41:04.500 --> 41:06.417
I didn't feel
comfortable driving.

41:06.417 --> 41:09.542
My ankle's hurting and I'm
still having nightmares.

41:11.000 --> 41:12.500
It might be the pills, but...

41:13.542 --> 41:14.417
What?

41:16.417 --> 41:19.417
I thought I heard a
man's voice last night.

41:19.417 --> 41:22.125
Probably
just a nightmare.

41:22.125 --> 41:24.917
Maybe. I don't know anymore.

41:26.292 --> 41:28.500
Well, are you sure
your alarm system's working?

41:28.500 --> 41:30.042
Yeah, Marcus checked it.

41:30.042 --> 41:32.167
Okay,
well get some rest

41:32.167 --> 41:34.292
and call me if
you need anything.

41:35.417 --> 41:37.917
Hey.

41:43.167 --> 41:44.375
Are you hungry?

41:45.542 --> 41:47.542
Come on.

41:48.542 --> 41:50.542
Yeah, there you go.

42:11.292 --> 42:12.167
Ugh. Hera.

42:13.167 --> 42:14.542
I'm the technician!

42:14.542 --> 42:17.042
I know! Just one sec!

42:17.042 --> 42:18.292
Ugh.

42:19.500 --> 42:20.375
Sorry.

42:21.417 --> 42:22.625
You called for the thermostat?

42:22.625 --> 42:24.542
I did. Thank you
for coming so soon.

42:24.542 --> 42:26.125
- No problem.
- Come in.

42:29.625 --> 42:31.042
I need
access to the main unit.

42:32.500 --> 42:33.500
It's in the laundry.

42:33.500 --> 42:34.375
I'll-
I know.

42:35.417 --> 42:37.000
You know?

42:37.000 --> 42:39.125
Yeah, I wired this place.
I knew the old owner.

42:39.125 --> 42:40.667
Oh. That's nice.

42:40.667 --> 42:43.250
Um, did he move away or...

42:43.250 --> 42:44.167
Nobody knows.

42:46.167 --> 42:47.542
One day, he just disappeared.

42:51.542 --> 42:53.292
It was really
hot this morning.

42:53.292 --> 42:56.292
Now it's freezing. I don't
know what's going on.

42:57.292 --> 42:58.125
Bless you.

42:59.542 --> 43:00.417
Thank you.

43:01.500 --> 43:02.667
Do you have a cat?

43:02.667 --> 43:03.542
Yeah, I do.

43:04.750 --> 43:08.542
He's probably in here. He
loves sleeping in the washer.

43:08.542 --> 43:10.417
Hello.

43:10.417 --> 43:12.417
I'm allergic.

43:12.417 --> 43:13.625
Oh.

43:13.625 --> 43:15.417
Sleeping in there's
dangerous, kitty.

43:19.417 --> 43:22.292
Looks like this little
thing here got burned out.

43:22.292 --> 43:23.542
We need to change it.

43:23.542 --> 43:25.667
Okay. How long
is that gonna take?

43:25.667 --> 43:27.667
I don't
have a new one with me.

43:27.667 --> 43:30.000
I can come back tomorrow.

43:30.000 --> 43:33.542
Sure. Okay, but the burglar
alarm, that works, right?

43:34.667 --> 43:36.417
Yeah. This is
for the HVAC unit.

43:39.292 --> 43:41.292
Um, can I have a glass of water?

43:42.167 --> 43:43.542
Sure. Right this way.

43:55.167 --> 43:56.292
There you go.

44:04.417 --> 44:05.292
Thank you.

44:06.500 --> 44:08.167
You're welcome.
I'll show you out.

44:39.542 --> 44:41.667
Hey, Dr. Tate.

44:41.667 --> 44:43.375
Hey, Julie. How are you?

44:44.792 --> 44:48.042
Um, oh, wait. Hera, turn
off the sound in this room.

44:50.667 --> 44:51.542
Hera?

44:56.167 --> 44:58.500
Turning off sound now.

44:58.500 --> 44:59.417
Is
that your husband's

44:59.417 --> 45:01.417
virtual assistant program?

45:01.417 --> 45:02.417
Yeah.

45:02.417 --> 45:03.667
How do you like it?

45:03.667 --> 45:04.667
It's fine.

45:04.667 --> 45:07.500
So have you
been since Marcus left?

45:08.667 --> 45:10.125
Not great.

45:10.125 --> 45:15.042
Uh, I don't like being
alone, I'm not sleeping,

45:16.167 --> 45:20.042
and I thought I heard
voices last night.

45:21.250 --> 45:22.542
What do you mean
you heard voices?

45:22.542 --> 45:25.167
I don't know, I thought
I heard glass breaking

45:26.625 --> 45:28.250
and someone calling my name.

45:30.792 --> 45:33.167
I don't know, it scared
me half to death.

45:34.500 --> 45:37.417
Could it
have been a bad dream?

45:37.417 --> 45:39.792
It could have. I'm not sure.

45:41.292 --> 45:42.625
Hmm, had
you taken your medication

45:42.625 --> 45:44.542
or did you have any alcohol?

45:44.542 --> 45:46.625
No, last night, I just...

45:46.625 --> 45:49.417
I took my pain meds
and a sleeping pill.

45:49.417 --> 45:53.167
Oh, well, sometimes,
combination of poor sleep

45:53.167 --> 45:55.292
and the stress of
being alone combined

45:55.292 --> 45:57.667
with mixed medication
can cause our minds

45:57.667 --> 45:58.875
to play tricks on us.

45:59.917 --> 46:01.875
But it felt so real.

46:03.417 --> 46:05.792
What else can
you tell me about last night?

46:05.792 --> 46:08.292
Well, look, it's been...

46:25.000 --> 46:29.750
There's this old
saying, "Art isn't finished-

46:29.750 --> 46:31.625
Only abandoned.

46:31.625 --> 46:33.500
I'm glad
you've heard it too.

46:33.500 --> 46:34.750
Same goes with therapy.

46:35.875 --> 46:36.750
Don't give up.

46:39.667 --> 46:41.792
Hi, Julie.
How's it going?

46:44.250 --> 46:47.625
You're up early.
What time is it there?

46:47.625 --> 46:50.500
There
where? I'm here.

46:50.500 --> 46:52.250
Okay.

46:52.250 --> 46:55.542
Stop messing around,
okay, Marcus? Please.

46:55.542 --> 46:57.292
You
don't like to play?

46:58.667 --> 47:00.292
It's not funny.

47:00.292 --> 47:01.292
You know I hate talking to
you through the cameras.

47:01.292 --> 47:05.667
Can you please just call
me like a normal person?

47:05.667 --> 47:08.375
Wanna
play hide and seek?

47:21.542 --> 47:24.500
Come on, let's play.

47:24.500 --> 47:27.292
You've reached
Marcus. Please leave a message.

47:27.292 --> 47:28.667
What?

47:30.667 --> 47:32.792
You've reached
Marcus. Please leave a message.

47:32.792 --> 47:36.667
He's probably
