50:40.125 --> 50:41.042
A man's voice.

50:41.042 --> 50:42.875
Did you see anybody?

50:42.875 --> 50:44.042
No, I didn't. I, um,

50:44.042 --> 50:47.542
I thought it was my husband
messing around, but it wasn't.

50:47.542 --> 50:48.917
And, um, I-

50:48.917 --> 50:50.667
I'll go check
it out. You stay here.

50:50.667 --> 50:52.792
Okay. Thank you.

50:55.750 --> 50:57.750
I'll turn off the alarm.

53:36.667 --> 53:38.125
So?

53:38.125 --> 53:40.875
