ma'am, except for your cat.

53:40.875 --> 53:42.250
Almost gave me a heart attack.

53:43.250 --> 53:45.292
No, that's
impossible. I heard him.

53:45.292 --> 53:47.292
And, I mean, the lights.

53:54.042 --> 53:55.167
Can we please just...

53:56.167 --> 53:57.292
Please have another look.

53:58.292 --> 53:59.917
Sure.

53:59.917 --> 54:03.042
Thank you. I swear, I
heard him loud and clear.

54:04.792 --> 54:06.792
Well, you know, these devices,

54:06.792 --> 54:09.917
they can get crossed
up with radio signals.

54:09.917 --> 54:11.667
Might have just
been a bored kid.

54:12.792 --> 54:14.792
We got plenty of those
around, trust me.

54:14.792 --> 54:16.292
You wouldn't be the
first one to be pranked.

54:16.292 --> 54:19.292
But he knew my name.

54:19.292 --> 54:20.917
You're new here.

54:20.917 --> 54:23.042
And people around here,

54:23.042 --> 54:25.292
everybody knows everybody
else's business.

54:25.292 --> 54:27.292
There's just not
much else to do.

54:28.917 --> 54:31.167
I'm telling you, kids with
not enough distractions

54:31.167 --> 54:32.792
can get pretty creative.

54:34.167 --> 54:36.625
Wait, he sent me texts.

54:37.292 --> 54:39.042
Here.

54:39.042 --> 54:39.917
See?

54:41.667 --> 54:43.917
All right. What
am I looking at?

54:45.917 --> 54:47.375
The messages.

54:47.375 --> 54:48.792
He sent me these...

54:50.917 --> 54:53.792
What? They were here.

54:53.792 --> 54:54.667
I...

54:57.167 --> 55:01.292
You know, maybe you
should try to get some rest.

55:01.292 --> 55:03.792
Might have just had a
little too much to drink.

55:07.167 --> 55:08.042
Well...

55:10.792 --> 55:13.667
I mean, we've been through
the whole house twice. Nobody.

55:16.417 --> 55:18.292
I don't know about
the text messages.

55:20.667 --> 55:24.292
Listen, be sure to
turn on the alarm, huh?

55:24.292 --> 55:26.375
We don't have any serious
trouble around here,

55:26.375 --> 55:29.375
but better be safe than sorry.

55:29.375 --> 55:30.750
Okay.

55:30.750 --> 55:31.417
Oh.

55:33.375 --> 55:34.750
It's my husband.

55:34.750 --> 55:36.042
You have a good night.

55:36.042 --> 55:37.042
Thank you.

55:45.375 --> 55:46.792
Where were you?

55:46.792 --> 55:49.000
Yeah, sorry,
I was in a meeting.

55:49.000 --> 55:49.875
What's going on?

55:50.750 --> 55:51.875
Someone was in the house.

55:51.875 --> 55:53.125
What? Who?

55:53.125 --> 55:54.875
- I heard him.
- Wait, where?

55:54.875 --> 55:56.292
Wait. Hold on.

55:56.292 --> 56:00.125
I heard a voice, a male
voice through the cameras.

56:00.125 --> 56:01.292
I'm pulling
up the cameras.

56:01.292 --> 56:02.792
I thought it was just
you messing around,

56:02.792 --> 56:05.042
but then when you
didn't pick up-

56:05.042 --> 56:07.042
Well, I can see
that the police were there.

56:07.042 --> 56:08.542
What did they say?

56:08.542 --> 56:11.417
Yeah, Hera called him, but
he couldn't find anybody.

56:12.917 --> 56:14.167
Well, I don't
see anything on the footage.

56:14.167 --> 56:16.417
Where are you?

56:16.417 --> 56:18.167
I only
hear you screaming.

56:18.167 --> 56:19.792
Well, Hera will tell you.

56:19.792 --> 56:23.042
Hera, you heard it,
right? You heard him?

56:23.042 --> 56:24.417
I'm afraid Not, Julie.

56:24.417 --> 56:27.167
My system experienced
a brief interruption,

56:27.167 --> 56:29.917
