just to be safe.

56:31.042 --> 56:33.792
Marcus, you swear
you don't hear anybody?

56:35.167 --> 56:36.042
No.

56:37.000 --> 56:38.417
I swear I didn't hear anything.

56:38.417 --> 56:41.875
Wait, could that
technician have messed

56:41.875 --> 56:43.250
with the system somehow?

56:43.250 --> 56:45.917
But why
would he do that?

56:45.917 --> 56:47.792
I mean, I didn't even know
if he knows how to do that.

56:47.792 --> 56:48.917
He's an HVAC technician.

56:48.917 --> 56:49.917
I just...

56:49.917 --> 56:51.125
I don't understand.

56:53.625 --> 56:55.417
Well, the cop said that
it could have been kids

56:55.417 --> 56:57.792
in the area playing
with radio equipment.

56:57.792 --> 56:59.417
Okay, well,
yeah, we can look into that,

56:59.417 --> 57:04.292
but I don't see how that
could happen, if it happened.

57:05.792 --> 57:08.292
- You don't believe me.
- Julie, Julie,

57:08.292 --> 57:09.875
I think that you
experienced something

57:09.875 --> 57:12.000
and Hera even said that
there was some interference,

57:12.000 --> 57:13.792
so we'll figure it out.

57:13.792 --> 57:16.542
But you're safe, I promise.

57:16.542 --> 57:20.375
How about you take a pill
and you try to relax?

57:20.375 --> 57:21.917
You can call me if
you need anything.

57:21.917 --> 57:23.542
I'll make sure my
phone's on, okay?

57:24.792 --> 57:26.417
- Okay.
- Okay.

57:26.417 --> 57:27.375
- I will.
- Bye.

57:28.417 --> 57:30.792
Bye.

57:36.417 --> 57:37.292
Pepper.

57:41.000 --> 57:42.167
Sergeant Pepper?

58:55.042 --> 58:56.917
Hi.
Ooh!

58:56.917 --> 58:59.250
